description: Oklahoma City is going crazy for the scrumptious stuffed pancakes they're makin' at Bacon N' Cakin'.This truck is serving up a selection of savory & sweet pancake perfection. Come out and chow down on the Hound Dog with peanut butter, bacon, and bananas. And if it’s early and you’re still coming out of that dreamy daze, the Strawberries & Cream just may be the pick-me-up pancakes for you. So if you're craving the most important meal any time of the day, then you gotta shake your way straight to Bacon N’ Cakin’!
name: Bacon N' Cakin'
